User Component:
================

Users:
1. ID + Public_ID
2. F/L Name
3. Username
4. Email
5. Password
6. Age
7. Exp.
8. Skills (IDs -> m2m relationship)
9. Profile (ID -> m2m relationship; macro-system; multiple roles)
10. Role (ID -> m2m relationship; micro-system)
11. Manager
12. Team
13. Department
14. Date of Birth
15. Contract
17. Phone
18. 3rd Party Accounts (LinkedIn, Facebook, yahoo...)

Contract:
1. ID + Public_ID
2. Start Date
*3. End Date
4. Salary
5. Job Type (Fulltime / parttime / hourly)
6. Paid Personal Time
7. Benefits
8. Review Reccurency

Benefits:
1. ID + Public_ID
2. Name
3. Description
4. Attachment

Skills:
1. ID + Public_ID
2. Name
3. Type (Tech skill, soft skill)
4. Description

Review:
1. ID + Public_ID
2. Reviewer
3. Reviewee
4. Review Type (Skill / Question)
5. Skill reviewed
*6. Grade
*7. Question
*8. Answer

Team:
1. ID + Public_ID
2. Name
3. Description
4. Icon
5. Projects (m2m relationship)
6. Members
7. Team Lead
8. Manager
9. Department

Department
1. ID
2. Name
3. Description
4. Type (Software, Hardware, Legal, Admin...)
5. Teams

Roles:
1. ID
2. Name
3. Description
4. Rights (m2m relationship; READ, WRITE, EXECUTE, DELETE)
5. Profiles (m2m relationship)

UserEntityRightRelation:
1. ID
2. UserID
3. Right
4. EntityType (Project, Sprint, Task, etc.)
5. EntityID

Profiles:
1. ID
2. Owner
3. UserID
4. Right
5. EntityType
6. EntityID
